These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
2 different games are played: chess, go
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, biathlon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the dancer##8
3. the owner of the rat is not the montecristo-smoker##6
4. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
5. the mechanic is not to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
7. the person playing chess is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | coffee      |
| Game          | go | chess   |
| Pet         | rat    | cat |
| Job           | dancer     | mechanic    |
| Cigar   | game    | montecristo       |
| Sport   | soccer    | biathlon        |
| Flower     | balloon-flower     | lily        |

